---
title: Cheesy Double BBQ Chicken Pizza with Tomato Salad
description: Who needs a takeaway shop when homedame pizza tastes this good? Unleash your inner chef with this recipe, roll your own dough, and arrange the toppings just how you like! BBQ sauce, chicken and onion act as the perfect ingredients to create your very own masterpiece.
